The,YouMail,Spam,Risk,API,filters,incoming,calls,and,detects,spamming,numbers,The,RESTful,API,returns,approval,and,cautionary,signals,confirming,whether,a,number,is,a,spam,a,likely,spam,or,not,spam,This,way,users,can,conveniently,block,robocallers,and,other,spamming,numbers,Its,lightweight,architecture,supports,high,speed,analysis,and,processing,of,requests,that,are,returned,in,JSON,and,XML,formatted,responses